.TH "mds-compiler" "1" "July 2014" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
mds-compiler \- Compiler for processors, microcontrolles, etc. used by the Multitarget Development System by Moravia Microsystems, s.r.o.
.SH USAGE
.B mds-compiler <OPTIONS> <path-to-source> [ <path-to-source> ... ]

.RB [ \-\-help ]
.RB [ \-h ]
.RB [ \-\-assemble
.IR asm_file ]
.RB [ \-\-compile
.IR asm_file ]
.RB [ \-\-iram\-size
.IR size ]
.RB [ \-\-code\-size
.IR size ]
.RB [ \-\-xram\-size
.IR size ]
.RB [ \-\-no\-opt ]
.RB [ \-\-quiet ]
.RB [ \-q ]
.RB [ \-\-nosplash ]
.RB [ \-\-nocolor ]
.RB [ \-n ]
.RB [ \-\-version ]
.RB [ \-V ]
.RB [ \-\-defaults ]
.RB [ \-\-disassemble ]
.RB [ \-\-minimalized ]
.RB [ \-\-config\-file
.IR filename ]
.RB [ \-\-check\-libraries ]
.RB [ \-\-ignore\-last\-session ]
.RB [ \-\-open\-project
.IR project ]
.RB [ \-\-reset\-user\-settings ]
.RB [ \-\-hex2bin
.IR input
.IR output ]
.RB [ \-\-bin2hex
